layout: layouts/base-finpay.njk
title: "Unlock Your 401k's Hidden Feature — Self-Directed Brokerage | Capital Wealth"
description: "Your employer's 401k likely includes a Self-Directed Brokerage Account (SDBA) — giving you access to thousands of investments beyond your plan's default menu. Professional fiduciary management from Capital Wealth. Complimentary strategy call."
noindex: true
